   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>From the <uicontrol>Main Menu</uicontrol>, select <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Event Log</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>View Statistic</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> using the UP/DOWN keys and the ENTER key. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Use the UP/DOWN keys to browse through the statistics available
on the UPS.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
